                <p>The second season of Prime Video's Fallout TV series is almost here, and to celebrate, <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Xbox+Fallout+Pip-Boy+Controller+Is+Now+Available+To+Preorder&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-11+04%3A46%3A16&amp;fnarticle_id=6536863&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3D6%2F8cehJ%2FO8c%26mid%3D24542%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Wireless-Controller-Fallout-Pip-Boy%2F8mzbmmcjzpp1%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fxbox-fallout-pip-boy-controller-is-now-available-to-preorder%2F1100-6536863%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Microsoft has revealed a new Xbox controller</a> that looks like it came straight out of the radioactive wasteland. Currently a timed exclusive through the Microsoft Store, the Fallout Pip-Boy Xbox controller is now available to order for $83 (was $99). If you want to add some flair, you can also customize the controller through the <a href="https://xboxdesignlab.xbox.com/configure/xbox-wireless-controller?recipeId=EZNL4GTS&amp;FalloutPipBoyPMP_Hero_WLC" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Xbox Design Labs</a>, which lets you choose button styles, upgrade to metallic triggers and D-pads, rubberize the side and back grips, and add an engraving.</p><div title="6536863 -- Xbox Wireless Controller – Fallout Pip-Boy" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="5230" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6536863 -- Xbox Wireless Controller – Fallout Pip-Boy" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Xbox+Fallout+Pip-Boy+Controller+Is+Now+Available+To+Preorder&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2025-12